00:05:07.370 --> 00:05:10.130 align:middle line:10%
such as courage and
integrity, and learning how

00:05:10.130 --> 00:05:13.310 align:middle line:10%
to rely on your values in life.

00:05:13.310 --> 00:05:15.230 align:middle line:10%
And the third level
of self-esteem

00:05:15.230 --> 00:05:17.390 align:middle line:10%
is mystical self-esteem.

00:05:17.390 --> 00:05:20.840 align:middle line:10%
That's the capacity to rely
