00:05:23.480 --> 00:05:27.230 align:middle line:10%
a harmonious balance between
your interior and exterior

00:05:27.230 --> 00:05:28.760 align:middle line:10%
consciousness.

00:05:28.760 --> 00:05:30.800 align:middle line:90%
