00:05:33.710 --> 00:05:36.320 align:middle line:84%
transforming for
others than anything

00:05:36.320 --> 00:05:37.880 align:middle line:90%
an ordinary person does.

00:05:37.880 --> 00:05:41.360 align:middle line:90%


00:05:41.360 --> 00:05:46.160 align:middle line:84%
We're discovering the
power of our nature.

00:05:46.160 --> 00:05:50.280 align:middle line:84%
This is such a great,
big, huge, big deal.

00:05:50.280 --> 00:05:53.750 align:middle line:84%
It's so huge that it doesn't
even fit in our heads.

00:05:53.750 --> 00:06:01.250 align:middle line:84%
This explains so
much why in this era,

00:06:01.250 --> 00:06:04.520 align:middle line:90%
we have become hypersensitive.

00:06:04.520 --> 00:06:06.890 align:middle line:84%
We think that
everything we say has

00:06:06.890 --> 00:06:09.920 align:middle line:90%
to be examined and processed.

00:06:09.920 --> 00:06:13.400 align:middle line:84%
And we become hypersensitive
about every word

00:06:13.400 --> 00:06:14.570 align:middle line:90%
said to us and everything.

00:06:14.570 --> 00:06:16.650 align:middle line:90%
But there's a reason for that.

00:06:16.650 --> 00:06:23.830 align:middle line:84%
The reason is because
in a different way,

00:06:23.830 --> 00:06:30.420 align:middle line:84%
we have to learn about how
powerful we are, how much power

00:06:30.420 --> 00:06:35.190 align:middle line:84%
is packed into
every word we say,

00:06:35.190 --> 00:06:44.590 align:middle line:84%
into every thought we have, into
how potent every single choice

00:06:44.590 --> 00:06:49.440 align:middle line:90%
we make is, how potent we are.

00:06:49.440 --> 00:06:54.970 align:middle line:84%
We are literally in a discovery
